_planning/

# Paper preparation directory — manuscript drafts, revision summaries, reviewer
# feedback, LaTeX/PDF builds, submission packages, in-flight statistical analyses.
# Not for public consumption; arXiv preprint and venue submission are the public
# artifacts. Experimental data referenced via ~/scratch/paap-v0.3-* paths.
_paper-prep/

# Anything explicitly marked private
*.private.md
*.draft.md
